<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Rules' }) %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<main class="page-main">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label reveal">The Law</div>
      <h1 class="page-title reveal">Server <span class="glow-text">Rules</span></h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="rules-list">
        <div class="rule reveal">
          <div class="rule-num">01</div>
          <div class="rule-body">
            <h3>Respect all players</h3>
            <p>In-game conflict is encouraged. Personal attacks, hate speech, and harassment are not. There is a difference between a war and harassment. Know it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rule reveal">
          <div class="rule-num">02</div>
          <div class="rule-body">
            <h3>No cheating or unfair mods</h3>
            <p>No hacked clients, X-ray, auto-clickers, or any modifications that give an unfair advantage. Optifine, shaders, and performance mods are fine.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rule reveal">
          <div class="rule-num">03</div>
          <div class="rule-body">
            <h3>No outside-game coordination during sessions</h3>
            <p>During active sessions, all coordination must happen in-game. No Discord calls with enemies. No sharing maps or coordinates externally.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rule reveal">
          <div class="rule-num">04</div>
          <div class="rule-body">
            <h3>Attend your sessions</h3>
            <p>You are committing to 10 sessions. Missing sessions without notice affects the whole event. If you can't attend, notify staff in advance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rule reveal">
          <div class="rule-num">05</div>
          <div class="rule-body">
            <h3>No griefing beyond what the game allows</h3>
            <p>Raiding, looting, and destroying enemy builds during conflict is part of the game. Senseless destruction of unclaimed neutral land is not.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rule reveal">
          <div class="rule-num">06</div>
          <div class="rule-body">
            <h3>Staff decisions are final</h3>
            <p>Staff may intervene in situations not covered by these rules. Their decisions are final. You may appeal through proper channels, not by arguing mid-session.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/foot') %>
